# SameDesk SwiftFormat config — deliberately conservative.
#
# Philosophy: apply the purely-cosmetic, safe cleanups (import sorting,
# indentation, trailing whitespace, stray leading blank lines) but PRESERVE the
# codebase's hand-tuned style — concise one-liner bodies, explicit `self` and
# `return`, `&&` in conditions, argument labels, digit grouping, and the
# hand-wrapped multi-line call sites. Reconciled with .swiftlint.yml so the two
# tools never fight (no trailing commas; braces stay on the same line).

--swiftversion 6.0

# --- Preserve concise one-liner bodies (CLAUDE.md mandate) ----------------------
--disable wrapFunctionBodies       # keep `func f() { body }`
--disable wrapPropertyBodies       # keep `var x: T { body }`
--disable wrapLoopBodies           # keep `for x in xs { body }`
--disable wrapMultilineStatementBraces

# --- Leave signatures, self, returns, and concurrency annotations alone ---------
--disable redundantSelf            # explicit `self.` is deliberate here
--disable redundantReturn          # keep explicit `return`
--disable redundantType            # keep explicit `: T = T(...)`
--disable redundantSendable        # leave concurrency annotations alone
--disable redundantViewBuilder
--disable unusedArguments          # keep labels like `_ notification: Notification`

# --- Don't rewrite operators / patterns / hand-wrapped arguments ----------------
--disable andOperator              # keep `a && b`, never `a, b`
--disable hoistPatternLet
--disable hoistTry
--disable preferKeyPath            # keep `{ $0.foo }` closures
--disable wrapArguments            # keep hand-aligned multi-line call sites
--disable docComments              # don't rewrite `//` into `///`
--disable consecutiveSpaces        # keep aligned trailing comments
--disable blankLinesBetweenScopes  # don't inject blank lines between members
--disable trailingCommas           # reconciled with SwiftLint

# --- Don't reflow numbers or ranges --------------------------------------------
--decimalgrouping ignore           # keep `48_000`
--binarygrouping ignore
--hexgrouping ignore
--octalgrouping ignore
--ranges nospace                   # keep `0..<n`

# --- Excludes ------------------------------------------------------------------
--exclude .build,Sources/SameDesk/Client/client.js,Sources/SameDesk/Client/client.html
